#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

int main (){
    
    int T, a, b, c, d, u, v, x, y, Tx, Ty, Lx, Ly;
    cin >> T;
    for (int k=0; k<T; k++){
        cin >> a >> b >> c >> d;
        cin >> u >> v >> x >> y;
        
        if (a <= x && d >= v){ // there is intersection
                 if (b >= v ){
                       if (a <= u){
                             Tx = u;
                             Ty = b;
                       }else{
                             Tx = a;
                             Ty = b;
                       }
                 }else{
                       if (a <= u){
                             Tx = u;
                             Ty = y;
                       }else{
                             Tx = a;
                             Ty = v;
                       }
                 }
                 if (y >= d){
                       if (x >= c){
                             Lx = c;
                             Ly = d;
                       }else{
                             Lx = c;
                             Ly = x;
                       }
                 }else{
                       if (x >= c){
                             Lx = c;
                             Ly = y;
                       }else{
                             Lx = x;
                             Ly = y;
                       }
                 }
                 
                 cout << Tx << " " << Ty << " " << Lx << " " << Ly << endl;
        }else{
              cout << "No Overlap" << endl;
        }
    }
    
    //system ("pause");
    return 0;
}
